window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Now stronger than ever, Salvos finally returns from the Bloodied Gulf!</b></p> <p>After learning a Grand Skill thanks to her father's unconventional training, it was time to depart for the human lands. Much has happened since she was gone. For one, demons are running wild and hunting her companions. For another, everything else has become so much...weaker.</p> <p><i>Grand Skill</i> is book six in the Salvos series.</p>"; 
